{"tid":889473,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"珍奶 x 拉麵？台灣高雄拉麵店推台日混血珍珠拉麵","createTime":"2018-11-04T14:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T08:58:39.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6464b5a8cf7b8d07863a0e4806a56f7a2d6072ff","tid":889473,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2200114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2200114&d=BceRMzIzTQxwWEDj4COd1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f0395d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2200114</a><br />\n珍珠奶茶是台灣知名的地道飲品，近年珍珠奶茶熱潮更擴散至日本和歐美地區。最近台灣高雄「極道ラーメン」拉麵店，更在 Facebook 專頁內宣傳新推出的「台日混血珍珠拉麵」，將台灣飲品和日本麵食精髓來個 Crossover！<br />\n<br />\n根據店方的描述，「台日混血珍珠拉麵」以「鮮奶茶的圓潤口感做為湯底，配上珍珠もちもちの新食感，就此誕生顛覆你的想像！珍奶也可以這&middot;樣&middot;吃&mdash;」作為賣點。從店方提供的食物相片中，可見該拉麵上擺放了日式叉燒、蔥花、竹荀、溏心蛋和海苔等常見拉麵配料，再於拉麵中央放置了大量珍珠。為了配合拉麵的味道，珍珠是特製的鹹味珍珠。「台日混血珍珠拉麵」在 11 月 2 日開售後，在開店 2 小時內已售罄，反應熱烈。<br />\n==========================<br />\n好想試呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e95499425ca30fc9863c6d1c6bc637c03bad6a9","tid":889473,"uid":200606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌，你食埋我個份，又咸又甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3bb860c2ca7be1c4f15d675b6f356be613a827","tid":889473,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e95499425ca30fc9863c6d1c6bc637c03bad6a9","tid":889473,"uid":200606,"like":0,"